{"tid":1616983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實閒日應該同狗打消耗戰","createTime":"2019-10-03T15:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T15:26:39.000Z","uid":31303,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6fdf16c1094123665cb81c53f5cec76847cda763","tid":1616983,"uid":31303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:07:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">星期一至五</span><br />\n<br />\n街坊做野 你地落樓方便<br />\n<br />\n快閃完 引到d狗出黎就散水<br />\n<br />\n狗仔返狗屋 又再落返黎引狗<br />\n<br />\n周而復始<br />\n<br />\n等d狗仔出到黎人又拉唔到 <br />\n<br />\n又唔可以係狗屋入面舒舒服服逗人工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">星期六 日</span><br />\n<br />\n先和理非 再勇武<br />\n<br />\n因為星期一至五既街頭消耗戰<br />\n<br />\n各區狗仔都疲於奔命<br />\n<br />\n中午又有各理非要處理<br />\n<br />\n到晚上勇武做野都易d"},{"pid":"ccc87c60f7ac04607e6d4a52f290cd86e5ab33b0","tid":1616983,"uid":31303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:08:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef09330a6683b192b21c56aea6f01d37685b8928","tid":1616983,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:09:10.000Z","msg":"#請廣傳 <br />\n<br />\n香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會聽日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=b705c941\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"38e53cad6f485006e201858cb13c2b4b2c3398b5","tid":1616983,"uid":31303,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"呢兩日原來都好順利 但係就總係有街坊戀戰<br />\n<br />\n屌狗 唱歌 <br />\n<br />\n搞到比人拉"},{"pid":"1c8af5a11214d3c